```csharp
// LocalizationMiddleware.cs
// Localization iÃ§in middleware

namespace ResidenceManagement.API.Middleware
{
    public class LocalizationMiddleware
    {
        private readonly RequestDelegate _next;
        private readonly ILocalizationService _localizationService;
        
        public LocalizationMiddleware(RequestDelegate next, ILocalizationService localizationService)
        {
            _next = next;
            _localizationService = localizationService;
        }
        
        public async Task InvokeAsync(HttpContext context)
        {
            // HTTP isteÄŸinden tercih edilen dili alma (header, cookie veya querystring)
            string language = GetPreferredLanguage(context);
            
            // EÄŸer kullanÄ±cÄ± oturum aÃ§mÄ±ÅŸsa, kayÄ±tlÄ± dil tercihini kontrol et
            if (context.User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
            {
                int userId = int.Parse(context.User.FindFirst(ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier).Value);
                string userLanguage = await _localizationService.GetUserLanguagePreferenceAsync(userId);
                
                if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(userLanguage))
                {
                    language = userLanguage;
                }
            }
            
            // GeÃ§erli kÃ¼ltÃ¼rÃ¼ ayarla
            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(language))
            {
                CultureInfo culture = new CultureInfo(language);
                CultureInfo.CurrentCulture = culture;
                CultureInfo.CurrentUICulture = culture;
                
                // Dil tercihini response header'a ekle
                context.Response.Headers.Add("Content-Language", language);
            }
            
            // Ä°ÅŸlem zincirinde devam et
            await _next(context);
        }
        
        private string GetPreferredLanguage(HttpContext context)
        {
            // Accept-Language header'dan dil tercihini alÄ±r
            string language = context.Request.Headers["Accept-Language"].ToString().Split(',').FirstOrDefault();
            
            // Query string'den dil tercihi kontrolÃ¼
            string queryLang = context.Request.Query["lang"].ToString();
            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(queryLang))
            {
                language = queryLang;
            }
            
            // Cookie'den dil tercihi kontrolÃ¼
            string cookieLang = context.Request.Cookies["PreferredLanguage"];
            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(cookieLang))
            {
                language = cookieLang;
            }
            
            return language;
        }
    }
}
```

```diff
+             
+             var query = _context.MaintenanceSchedules
+                 .Where(m => m.ScheduledDate >= DateTime.Now && m.ScheduledDate <= endDate)
+                 .AsQueryable();

+             if (residenceId.HasValue)

+             var byTypeQuery = await query

+         // Maliyet raporunu getirme
+         public async Task<MaintenanceCostReportDTO> GetMaintenanceCostReportAsync(
+             DateTime startDate, DateTime endDate, int? residenceId)
+         {
+             var query = _context.MaintenanceSchedules
+                 .Where(m => m.CompletionDate >= startDate && m.CompletionDate <= endDate)
+                 .AsQueryable();
+ 
+             if (residenceId.HasValue)
+             {
+                 query = query.Where(m => m.ResidenceId == residenceId.Value);
+             }
+ 
+             // Tamamlanan bakÄ±m iÅŸlerini al
+             var completedMaintenances = await query
+                 .Where(m => m.Status == "TamamlandÄ±" && m.ActualCost.HasValue)
+                 .ToListAsync();
+ 
+             // Toplam ve ortalama maliyet hesapla
+             decimal totalCost = completedMaintenances.Sum(m => m.ActualCost.Value);
+             decimal averageCost = completedMaintenances.Count > 0 
+                 ? totalCost / completedMaintenances.Count 
+                 : 0;
+ 
+             // BakÄ±m tÃ¼rlerine gÃ¶re maliyet
+             var costByType = completedMaintenances
+                 .GroupBy(m => m.MaintenanceType)
+                 .Select(g => new
+                 {
+                     Type = g.Key,
+                     TotalCost = g.Sum(m => m.ActualCost.Value),
+                     Count = g.Count()
+                 })
+                 .OrderByDescending(x => x.TotalCost)
+                 .ToList();
+ 
+             // Ekipman tÃ¼rlerine gÃ¶re maliyet
+             var costByEquipment = completedMaintenances
+                 .Where(m => m.EquipmentId.HasValue)
+                 .GroupBy(m => m.EquipmentId)
+                 .Select(g => new
+                 {
+                     EquipmentId = g.Key.Value,
+                     TotalCost = g.Sum(m => m.ActualCost.Value),
+                     Count = g.Count()
+                 })
+                 .OrderByDescending(x => x.TotalCost)
+                 .ToList();
+ 
+             var report = new MaintenanceCostReportDTO
+             {
+                 StartDate = startDate,
+                 EndDate = endDate,
+                 TotalMaintenanceCount = completedMaintenances.Count,
+                 TotalCost = totalCost,
+                 AverageCost = averageCost,
+                 MostExpensiveMaintenanceId = completedMaintenances.Count > 0 
+                     ? completedMaintenances.OrderByDescending(m => m.ActualCost).First().Id 
+                     : 0,
+                 MostExpensiveMaintenanceCost = completedMaintenances.Count > 0 
+                     ? completedMaintenances.OrderByDescending(m => m.ActualCost).First().ActualCost.Value 
+                     : 0,
+                 CostByMaintenanceType = costByType.Select(x => new CostByTypeDTO
+                 {
+                     Type = x.Type,
+                     TotalCost = x.TotalCost,
+                     Count = x.Count,
+                     AverageCost = x.Count > 0 ? x.TotalCost / x.Count : 0
+                 }).ToList(),
+                 ReportGeneratedDate = DateTime.Now
+             };
+ 
+             return report;
+         }
+     }
```
